project_descr: Support to Public Finance Management and Institutional Development

outputs.output_descr:
the overall objective of this program is to improve the effectiveness of the Ministry of Finance's performance by instigating a strong inclusiveness organizational culture and a results-based capacity development of the staff while spearheading the institutionalization of strategic management and supporting the implementation of Egypt’s roadmap for the enhancement of public finance management. 
The program is based on the groundwork of preceding assistance projects received mainly from IMF, WB, UNDP and British Embassy and will focus on the following four areas:
?	MOF Institutional development
